Journal Phenomics

Phenomics is a new hybrid journal focusing on cutting-edge scientific advances in the emerging field of phenomics. The dedicated editorial team welcomes studies that advances peoples knowledge on phenomics, the study of phenome that is a set of measurable properties of physical, chemical and biological phenotypes of individuals and populations other than the genome. The journal is free of charge for none-Open Access publication and provides free access in 2021-22.
